    <item>
      <title>由于利率依然居高不下，美国货币基金不再担忧改革</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-money-funds-look-past-reform-angst-thanks-to-still-high-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国货币市场基金行业仍在享受美国长期高利率的推动，摆脱了与今年晚些时候生效的改革相关的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/us-money-funds-look-past-reform-angst-thanks-to-still-high-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:47:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲准备将巴塞尔银行交易规则推迟一年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/europe-poised-to-delay-basel-bank-trading-rules-by-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，欧盟将把全球银行资本规则的关键部分推迟一年实施，以便欧盟银行机构不会因美国标准持续争论而处于不利地位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/europe-poised-to-delay-basel-bank-trading-rules-by-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 13:19:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国债券市场下跌，马克龙拒绝辞职传闻</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/macron-says-election-result-doesn-t-affect-president-s-position</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，他作为法国总统的地位不会受到立法选举结果的影响，因为他考虑辞职的一份报告引发了法国政府债券的抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/macron-says-election-result-doesn-t-affect-president-s-position</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 11:58:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Pimco 警告房地产市场受创 地区银行或将倒闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/pimco-warns-of-more-regional-bank-failures-on-commercial-property-pain</link>
      <description><![CDATA[太平洋投资管理公司预计，美国将会有更多地区性银行倒闭，因为这些银行的账面上存在的问题商业房地产贷款集中度“非常高”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/pimco-warns-of-more-regional-bank-failures-on-commercial-property-pain</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治风险影响银行股，法国股市再次下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/european-stocks-regain-ground-as-us-rates-take-focus-off-france</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙决定提前举行大选的影响不断加深，法国股市创下一年来最大两日跌幅，银行股和法国国债价格一同下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-11/european-stocks-regain-ground-as-us-rates-take-focus-off-france</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 07:13:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储决策前银行股遭遇抛售 市场重压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储公布利率决议前，银行股下跌令美国股市承压，欧洲政治不确定性促使交易员转向美国国债和美元等最安全的市场领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-10/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 22:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
